title: NFL ATL: Fantasy football extravaganza
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Fantasy football extravaganza
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview the 2014 fantasy football season by analyzing the average mock draft positions at quarterback, running back and wide receiver. Find out which players are being overhyped and who can be mid-round sleepers.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
